             born in the City of Antwerp, was indicted on the Statute for <rs id="t16761213-8-off24" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t16761213-8-off24" type="offenceCategory" value="miscellaneous"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t16761213-8-off24" type="offenceSubcategory" value="other"></interp>
